    <description>Cauline leaves 30–90 × 2–6 mm, reduced distally. Involucres 8–12 mm. Phyllary faces
        sparsely to moderately sericeous, sometimes sparsely stipitate-glandular distally. Ray
        florets 10–16; laminae 7–15. Disc florets 30–40; corollas 6.5–8.5 mm, lobes 0.6–0.8 mm,
        throats and lobes glabrous or proximal throats sparsely short-pilose. 2n = 36.</description>
